{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":"Juro por los [ángeles] enviados uno tras de otro,","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"77:2","price":"por los [ángeles] encargados de los vientos que soplan violentamente,","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"77:3","price":"por los [ángeles] que conducen y extienden las nubes,","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"77:4","price":"por los [ángeles] que distinguen claramente,","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"77:5","price":"por los [Profetas] que transmiten Mensajes","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُلۡقِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5627,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"77:6","price":"como aclaración o advertencia [para el Día del Juicio].","arabic":"عُذۡرًا أَوۡ نُذۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5628,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"77:7","price":"Tengan certeza de que aquello con que se les advierte se cumplirá","arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5629,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"77:8","price":"cuando las estrellas pierdan su luz,","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5630,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"77:9","price":"cuando el cielo se resque